title: BATTLE FOR WINDHELM - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #5
description:
NORDS ON THE DEFENSE - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #5 - In part 4 we encountered many challenges in the west part of our kingdom.  But now that fight is right at our front door.  The Empire has marched a large army to our capital Windhelm.  There is no other option but to face them head on! Enjoy the video :D

Mod link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/the-elder-scrolls-total-war

Unofficial Patch: http://www.twcenter.net/forums/showthread.php?750685-Sub-mod-Unofficial-TES-Patch-1-3-DOWNLOAD-LINK

JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3
